The Royal Palm RV Park is small and friendly. We only have 7 sites with limited availability. Please see the Calendar. All sites have full hookups with 30 and 50 amp service. We have a laundry, free WIFI, two bathhouses, clubhouse with kitchen available for use, lending library and lots of nice people.Â
ALL ARE WELCOME TO JOIN OUR HAPPY HOUR AT THE TIKI HUT.Â
Open November 1 through April 30Â
Our minimum stay is 3 nights.Â
Check-in is from 1pm to 6pm. Please call to arrange another time if necessary
